Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎晚上好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好像我这一天还不够糟似的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}As if my day wasn't going badly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎原来是特雷弗·贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's Trevor Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看起来不太好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You don't seem to be doing very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎发生什么事了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are we looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼和黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampires and night creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎试图杀死整座城堡的人类难民\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}trying to kill a castle full of human refugees,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有楼上的疯子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and a madman upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎开始吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们终于快到了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Finally. We're nearly there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会在上面开个洞\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll need to create a hole in that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让棺材通过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to get the container through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不用了 我有我的办法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No need. I have skills too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先小小感受一下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just a little taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是很了不起的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, this is a remarkable thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎时间到了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The time approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你有赫克托的锻造咒语吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you have the forging phrases from Hector?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ah, Saint Germain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你从一开始就让我很愉悦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have been a joy to me from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很高兴你这么说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm delighted to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎果然是人类 这么容易被操控\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So human. So easily led.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,从我们之前见面开始就是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}From the moment we met face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们之前并没有见过面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't believe we've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎当然见过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你认识我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在你身边指引你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been with you for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎已经有一段时间了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Guiding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你认识我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们是老朋友了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're old friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们人类夺走了我所有的宝藏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you people all took my treasure from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎死神本尊吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Death itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那是我的宝藏 ‎你这个无耻的笨蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My treasure, you gawping little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉原本要以惊人的规模\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Dracula was going to bring death to this world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎将死亡带到这个世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}on a scale unimagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我永远做不到的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Something I could never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是幽灵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个世界特定的功能\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A function of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不能招兵买马\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't raise armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我无法与充满生机的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't fight an entire world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,世界战斗 ‎直至它灭亡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}teeming with life and bleed it to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他可以\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而你们杀死了他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And that was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不是你所了解的吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not a vampire as you understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎死亡 就是我的食粮\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Death is my meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而你们人类毁了德古拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you people broke him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我无法把他带回来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I can't bring him back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不是人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because I'm not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么只有人类的手才能触及地狱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why is it that only human hands can reach into hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不觉得这太奇怪了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't you think that's weirdly fucked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎虽然我做不到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但你可以\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为你们人类的贪婪和欲求\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In your human greed, your human need,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你会不计代价地将他带回来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you could and would do anything to bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你疯了 ‎他会变成同体者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're insane. He will be a Rebis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不再是你之前认识的那个人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not the man you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他会成为吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He will be a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎身体里困着他尖叫的妻子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with his own screaming wife trapped inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他会精神错乱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He will be deranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎会怒气无边\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}His rage will know no bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎史无前例的杀戮将会出现\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There will be murder on a scale never before seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会不断进食\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I will feed and become
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,成为这个世界上最强大的生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the strongest creature on this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以开始吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎完成它\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎会很有趣的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎否则我现在就杀了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or I'll kill you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这样你就再也见不到她了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you'll never, ever see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那是最后一个吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is that the last of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎希望如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bloody better be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赛珐 特雷弗 这是格丽塔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sypha, Trevor, this is Greta,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎离这里最近的村庄的首领\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}headwoman of the nearest village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些是她的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These are her people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你损失了多少人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How many did you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我正要去查个清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's what I'm going to find out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很高兴见到你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你刚刚在说楼上有个疯子吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You were saying something about a madman upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫圣日尔曼的混蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A little shit by the name of Saint Germain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的天 ‎那就是死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, my God. That is actually Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么 那是镰刀死神本尊吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What? That's supposed to be the Grim Reaper himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那就是死亡的样子吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's what death looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 死神 是它的名字\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, no, Death. It's the name it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's like a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只是它吸食的是我们的灵魂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}only it feeds on whatever leaves us when we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎家族记录称它是一种元素之灵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The family books called it an elemental spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎通过伪装来为权力服务\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that disguises itself to serve power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们看到一个年长的吸血鬼 ‎穿过传送门了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We saw an old vampire jump through the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那里面没有其他人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's no one else in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就是他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他可能是德古拉宫廷的成员\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He was probably part of Dracula's court.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎退后一点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Stand back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能感觉到空气在变化\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can feel the air changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们在移动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我闻到了人类的魔法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I smell the human magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没办法停下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I cannot stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎丽莎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们还活着吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are we alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我好像认得这个房间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think I recognize this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎太美好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别犹豫 德古拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let go, Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎疯狂吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎把能让我强大所需的一切都带过来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bring me everything I need to thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎屠杀这个世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Murder the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让我不再感到饥饿\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}just so I don't have to be hungry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的天呐\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我都做了什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Belmont!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,干点有用的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Make yourself useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎白痴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我爱你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎特雷弗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Trevor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你最好知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'd better know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎记住\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"特雷弗"这个名字很难听\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Trefor is a terrible name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎喂 ‎死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oi. Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想和你谈谈\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I want a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你认识我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是贝尔蒙特家族的特雷弗·贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm Trevor Belmont of House Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我当然认识你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们最擅长找东西和认东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Finding things and recognizing things is what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而你绝对是个"东西"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you are absolutely a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在地球生命的曙光中到来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was put here at the dawn of life on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:23:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎去吸食你们每一个愚蠢人类的最后一口气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to feed on the last breath of every one of you fuckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不只是个东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm a little more than a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 ‎你只是个东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. You're only a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你只是个年老的杀手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're only an old killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你无所事事 根本算不上活着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You don't make anything. You don't live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你只是吸食 躲藏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You just eat and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这有什么意义吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is there a point to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎贝尔蒙特 ‎你是在向我口述你那该死的讣告吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you dictating your fucking obituary to me, Belmont?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是时候把这个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's time to give this place back to people
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还给懂得建造的人类了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}who know how to build things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你和我 我们只是历史上的杀手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You and me, we're just killers out of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们该离开了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's time for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谁来逼我走呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And who's going to make me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎手里拿着铁链的你吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You, with your bit of string in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我们还是再试一次吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But let's just give this one last go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎开始吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.41,0:25:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个游戏很好玩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, this is a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.82,0:25:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎噢 他倒下了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, he fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.22,0:25:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要吃掉你的灵魂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm going to eat your soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.67,0:25:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再拉出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}shit it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.72,0:25:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后用它把你女朋友闷死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and use it to smother your fucking girlfriend to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.99,0:25:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.35,0:26:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而你只是个人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're just a human being.
